enfrewshire, Scotland, United Kingdom, his father, John Montgomery of Eaglesham and Eastwood 7th Lord of Eaglesham, was 56 and his mother, Janet Erskine, was 26. He married Margaret Douglas in 1334, in Eaglesham, Renfrewshire, Scotland. They were the parents of at least 1 son and 1 daughter. His occupation is listed as laird of eaglesham in Eaglesham, Renfrewshire, Scotland, United Kingdom. He died on 25 June 1388, in Eaglesham, Renfrewshire, Scotland, at the age of 84, and was buried in Eaglesham, Renfrewshire, Scotland."},"et":{"Abt 1305–25 June 1388":"umbes 1305–25. juuni 1388","1305–1388":"1305–1388","1312–Female":"1312–Surnud","1323–Male":"1323–Surnud","1328–1391":"1328–1391","–Male":"Surnud","1305–1374":"1305–1374","1334–Female":"1334–Surnud","1338–1398":"1338–1398","1250–1328":"1250–1328","1280–1360":"1280–1360","1374":"1374","25 June 1388":"25. juuni 1388","1360":"1360","1250":"1250","1391":"1391","1280":"1280","Abt 1305":"umbes 1305","1338":"1338","1305":"1305","1334":"1334","1323":"1323","1312":"1312","1388":"1388","1398":"1398","about 1300":"umbes 1300","1328":"1328","Scotland":"Scotland","Eaglesham, Renfrewshire, Scotland":"Eaglesham, Renfrewshire, Scotland"},"fi":{"Abt 1305–25 June 1388":"noin 1305–25. kesäkuuta 1388","1305–1388":"1305–1388","1312–Female":"1312–Kuollut","1323–Male":"1323–Kuollut","1328–1391":"1328–1391","–Male":"Kuollut","1305–1374":"1305–1374","1334–Female":"1334–Kuollut","1338–1398":"1338–1398","1250–1328":"1250–1328","1280–1360":"1280–1360","1374":"1374","25 June 1388":"25. kesäkuuta 1388","1360":"1360","1250":"1250","1391":"1391","1280":"1280","Abt 1305":"noin 1305","1338":"1338","1305":"1305","1334":"1334","1323":"1323","1312":"1312","1388":"1388","1398":"1398","about 1300":"noin 1300","1328":"1328","Scotland":"Scotland","Eaglesham, Renfrewshire, Scotland":"Eaglesham, Renfrewshire, Scotland"},"fr":{"Abt 1305–25 June 1388":"environ 1305–25 juin 1388","1305–1388":"1305–1388","1312–Female":"1312–Décédée","1323–Male":"1323–Décédé","132